Cipembedzo ndi cinthu cimene munthu amasankha monganso angasankhile zinthu, monga ndiwo za masamba, ngati wapiti ku maliketi.
Pali mau ambiri a anthu ena amene afuna kuti ena adzipembedzedwa, ndiye ncifukwa ninji tiona anthu ena kutama Yesu m’malo motama mwina Muhammad kapena Confucius, Buddha, kapena Charles Taze Russell kapena Joseph Smith.
